                "status": "active",
                "title": "Data Analyst",
                "description": "<h2>&nbsp;<\/h2><p><br>Main Responsibilities<br><br>1. Sales Performance Analysis<br>\u2022 Analyze sales by product, sales representative, territory\/region, and customer segment.<br>\u2022 Identify trends, opportunities, and performance gaps.<br>\u2022 Track achievement against sales targets and budgets.<br><br>2. Dashboard &amp; Reporting<br>\u2022 Create and maintain dashboards for management.<br>\u2022 Prepare daily sales reports, weekly performance reviews, monthly business reviews, and forecast reports.<br>\u2022 Ensure data accuracy and consistency.<br><br>3. Forecasting &amp; Planning<br>\u2022 Support sales forecasting.<br>\u2022 Analyze historical sales trends.<br>\u2022 Predict future demand and revenue.<br>\u2022 Help management set realistic targets.<br><br>4. Customer Analysis<br>\u2022 Analyze customer purchasing behavior.<br>\u2022 Identify high-value customers, customers at risk of leaving, and growth opportunities within accounts.<br>\u2022 Support customer segmentation strategies.<br><br>5. Pricing &amp; Profitability Analysis<br>\u2022 Analyze gross margins, product profitability, discount impact, and customer profitability.<br>\u2022 Recommend actions to improve profitability.<br><br>6. CRM &amp; Data Quality Management<br>\u2022 Monitor CRM data quality.<br>\u2022 Ensure opportunities, customer records, and sales activities are correctly recorded.<br>\u2022 Identify missing or inaccurate data.<br><br>7. Business Intelligence Support<br>\u2022 Build reports using Microsoft Power BI, Tableau, Microsoft Excel, and SQL Server.<br>\u2022 Automate reporting processes where possible.<br><br>Key KPIs for a Sales Data Analyst<br>\u2022 Report Accuracy %<br>\u2022 Dashboard Adoption Rate<br>\u2022 Forecast Accuracy %<br>\u2022 Data Quality Score<br>\u2022 Time Required to Generate Reports<br>\u2022 Number of Actionable Insights Implemented<br>\u2022 Revenue Opportunities Identified<br>\u2022 Margin Improvement Recommendations<br><br><br>&nbsp;<\/p>",
                "requirements": "<p>Bachelor's Degree in , Computer Science, Information Systems, Engineering, or a related field.&nbsp;<br>Professional certifications in Data Analytics, Business Intelligence, Power BI, SQL, or Data Science are a plus.&nbsp;<br><br>3\u20135 years of experience in Sales Analysis, Business Analysis, Commercial Excellence, Revenue Management, Business Intelligence, or a related analytical role.&nbsp;<br>Proven experience in analyzing sales performance, forecasting, budgeting, and KPI reporting.&nbsp;<br>Hands-on experience with Power BI, Microsoft Excel (Advanced), SQL, and CRM systems.&nbsp;<br>Experience developing dashboards, management reports, and automated reporting solutions.&nbsp;<br><br>Strong understanding of sales processes, pipeline management, pricing analysis, and profitability analysis.&nbsp;<br><br>Experience in healthcare, medical devices, pharmaceuticals, distribution, or FMCG industries is preferred.&nbsp;<\/p>",
